(firstQuint)Role of Bile Duct Resection in Major Hepatectomy Due to Intrahepatic Cholangiocarcinoma.

 The bile duct resection in hepatic lobectomy due to cholangiocarcinoma, mass forming type, is still controversial.

 We retrospectively evaluated the effect of bile duct resection in this surgery.

